{"tid":1029552,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"不要再輕視你的寂寞","createTime":"2019-02-20T10:12:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T15:57:12.000Z","uid":228854,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bc5d8bdfaa4c9f7bbac682a2443afdfa7fadc2fe","tid":1029552,"uid":228854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:12:57.000Z","msg":"想同大家分享一段片 <br />\n講人類點解會覺得寂寞同埋好好處理哩種情緒嘅重要性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有幾點係應該值得注意：<br />\n1）已經係毒撚/絲嘅你，再係坐喺度唔同人交流，只會變惡性循環，越變越毒，最後零社交甚至會演變成情緒病。<br />\n2）城市嘅普遍性係多咗寂寞心情嘅原因之一，多咗人忙碌於工作同埋離開自己本身嗰社交圈<br />\n3）寂寞係正常㗎！係生理需要，唔係你嘅錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最重要係你點處理哩種情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4）調查顯示出有好嘅社交技能唔代表你會有多啲朋友（豬朋狗友例外），唔會寂寞。無論你係毒撚社交撚都係一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/n3Xv_g3g-mA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fn3Xv_g3g-mA&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n82Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=48ef97f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/n3Xv_g3g-mA</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有好多論點我冇提及，歡迎討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358868b3e30d8e481a72dde93b29496ffa720d94","tid":1029552,"uid":228854,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:31:36.000Z","msg":"認真po無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪開喺健康台或者學術台會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n是但 推下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e095a64401337b2a21241517ebb55a056de472","tid":1029552,"uid":50321,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得最重要係 live with the pain <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多人會怕寂寞，就用社交網站去逃避，但係咁樣只會慢慢失去自己。<br />\n最好就專注係真實生活，先學識一個人獨處，培養下興趣等等，慢慢就自然會有途徑識朋友。<br />\n而當你唔再 care 係咪獨自一個人時，其實社交生活都會慢慢改善"},{"pid":"1597634e12e172934da49563d1169be8f7ea706d","tid":1029552,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:56:53.000Z","msg":"留名g持"},{"pid":"6cd23545ce7b8959ae8986ab66c05e56a1417b41","tid":1029552,"uid":228854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15e095a64401337b2a21241517ebb55a056de472","tid":1029552,"uid":50321,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得最重要係 live with the pain <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多人會怕寂寞，就用社交網站去逃避，但係咁樣只會慢慢失去自己。<br />\n最好就專注係真實生活，先學識一個人獨處，培養下興趣等等，慢慢就自然會有途徑識朋友。<br />\n而當你唔再 care 係咪獨自一個人時，其實社交生活都會慢慢改善"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T12:04:57.000Z","msg":"又係你呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你講得啱呀<br />\n問題只係當一個人太習慣自己一個毒，有時會搞到選擇性封閉自己。<br />\n就好似我自己，有時朋友叫我出嚟睇戲行街有幾次我都臨時放飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為自己懶得去social<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過有時候又會覺得寂寞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己攞嚟衰<br />\n要警惕下自己唔好咁樣，一個人過係開心，但係毒得太過份嘅時候就可能會出事<br />\n一定要聽你自己個心發出來嘅警號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32ea8c500a8aba2d956a8c3fbd3c431b41af404","tid":1029552,"uid":50321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cd23545ce7b8959ae8986ab66c05e56a1417b41","tid":1029552,"uid":228854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15e095a64401337b2a21241517ebb55a056de472","tid":1029552,"uid":50321,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得最重要係 live with the pain <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多人會怕寂寞，就用社交網站去逃避，但係咁樣只會慢慢失去自己。<br />\n最好就專注係真實生活，先學識一個人獨處，培養下興趣等等，慢慢就自然會